{"word":"Δαυλιάς","slug":"Δαυλιάς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n23549\" key=\"*daulia/s\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">Δαυλιάς</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, <sense id=\"n23549.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">woman of Daulis,</tr_> epith. of Procne, who was changed into <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">the nightingale,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:29\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.29</biblScope> </bibl> (<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Δαυλία κορώνη,</foreign> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Suid.</author> </bibl>); so her sister Philomela, changed into <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">the swallow,</tr_> was <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">Δαυλίς</orth>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.727d</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}